metadata.name: Supers Burn!
metadata.description:
Supers Burn Utility road to 2023 

Phase 1 - Supers Burn, you will reedem special gifts from Supers edition if you burn 2 editions.

Phase 2 - Free airdrop, you will get free airdrop for Supers edition holders.

Phase 3 - Raffle drop, all super edition holders you can get a chance to get a raffle drop in the next Supers edition.
